ething from the Ancients and from Maimonides—and not merely about them.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aHaskalah. 0aPhilosophy and religionxHistoryy20th century. 0aPhilosophy, GermanxHistoryy20th century. 4aJewish Studies : Jewish Philosophy. 4aPolitics and Law : Political Philosophy. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Political.2bisacsh1 aHowse, Robert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143844968540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438449685423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438449685/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles